<text><body>
<lb n="0652a07"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="0652a08"/>
<lb n="0652a09"/><head type="no">No. 1158</head>
<lb n="0652a10"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0652003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】享保年間刊豐山大學藏本，【甲】永久五年寫東山三密藏本</note>地藏菩薩儀軌</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0652a11"/>
<lb n="0652a12"/><byline type="Translator">中天竺輸婆迦羅奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0652a13"/><div1 type="jing"><p>爾時釋迦牟尼佛。在<note n="0652004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB14305;＝佉【甲】</note><app n="0652004"><lem>&CB14305;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">佉</rdg></app>羅提耶山。與無量諸
<lb n="0652a14"/><note n="0652005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔地藏〕－&M062485;【原】</note><sic n="0652005" corr="＆lac；" resp="【原】">地藏</sic>菩薩十俱胝比丘比丘尼及天龍八部
<lb n="0652a15"/>諸鬼神俱無量百千大眾圍繞而為說法。爾
<lb n="0652a16"/>時大眾中有一大士名曰地藏。<note n="0652006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔偏〕－【甲】</note><app n="0652006"><lem>偏</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>袒右肩右
<lb n="0652a17"/>膝著地。合掌恭敬白佛言。我說神&CB00057;欲利益
<lb n="0652a18"/>一切眾生。唯願世尊欲說神&CB00057;。慈哀聽許。時
<lb n="0652a19"/>佛告地藏菩薩言。汝等速說利益一切有情</p>
<lb n="0652a20"/><p>爾時地藏菩薩騰虛空讚歎歸命世尊。<note n="0652007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">在＝有【甲】</note><app n="0652007"><lem>在</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">有</rdg></app>空
<lb n="0652a21"/>中<note n="0652008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">亦＝示【甲】</note><app n="0652008"><lem>亦</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">示</rdg></app>現無量神通。以神口說&CB00057;曰</p>
<lb n="0652a22"/><p type="dharani">唵<note n="0652009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">闇＝閻&M062485;【原】，闇【甲】</note><note n="0652009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">闇＝閻&M062485;【原】，＝闇【甲】</note><app n="0652009"><lem><sic corr="閻" resp="【原】">闇</sic></lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">闇</rdg></app>摩他&CB03782;摩爾俱苾<note n="0652010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">俱苾＋（俱苾）【甲】</note><app n="0652010"><lem>俱苾</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">俱苾俱苾</rdg></app>三曼多<note n="0652011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">娑婆賀＝沙呵【甲】＊</note><app n="0652011"><lem>娑婆
<lb n="0652a23"/>賀</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">沙呵</rdg></app></p><p place="inline">次<note n="0652012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">說＝脫&M062485;【原】</note><sic n="0652012" corr="脫" resp="【原】">說</sic>心&CB00057;</p><p type="dharani">唵炎曼他<note n="0652013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00065;＝嗜【甲】</note><app n="0652013"><lem>&CB00065;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">嗜</rdg></app><app type="＊" source="0652011"><lem>娑婆賀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">沙呵</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0652a24"/><p><note n="0652014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">次＋（說）【甲】</note><app n="0652014"><lem>次</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">次說</rdg></app>心中心&CB00057;</p><p type="dharani">唵<note n="0652015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB03919;＝濕&M062485;【原】，砥&M062485;【原】，矷【甲】</note><note n="0652015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB03919;＝濕&M062485;【原】，砥&M062485;【原】，&CB03919;＝矷【甲】</note><app n="0652015"><lem>&CB03919;</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">矷</rdg></app><note n="0652015" place="foot" type="rest">&CB03919;＝濕&M062485;【原】，砥&M062485;【原】</note>呬<note place="inline">二合</note></p>
<lb n="0652a25"/><p>纔說此&CB00057;。十地等大菩薩。失本心迷惑。天龍
<lb n="0652a26"/>八部藥叉鬼神驚走倒地。日月星宿失光隱
<lb n="0652a27"/><note n="0652016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蔽＝弊【甲】</note><app n="0652016"><lem>蔽</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">弊</rdg></app><note n="0652017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">空雨＝雨空【甲】</note><app n="0652017"><lem>空。雨</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">雨空</rdg></app>寶華繽紛。窮劫說&CB00057;力不可說
<lb n="0652a28"/>盡</p>
<lb n="0652a29"/><p>次說畫像法。作聲聞形像。著袈裟端覆左肩。
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1158.0652b" n="0652b"/>
<lb n="0652b01"/>左手持盈華形。右手施無畏令坐蓮華。復<note n="0652018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（作）＋居【甲】</note><app n="0652018"><lem>居</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">作居</rdg></app>
<lb n="0652b02"/>座大士像頂著天冠著袈裟。左手持蓮華<note n="0652019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">茶＝葉&M062485;【原】，莖&M062485;【原】，坐【甲】</note><note n="0652019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">茶＝葉&M062485;【原】，莖&M062485;【原】，茶＝坐【甲】</note><app n="0652019"><lem>茶</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">坐</rdg></app><note n="0652019" place="foot" type="rest">茶＝葉&M062485;【原】，莖&M062485;【原】</note>。
<lb n="0652b03"/>右手如先令安坐九品蓮臺<note place="inline">傳云九品者九重<note n="0652020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔也亦…也〕八字－【甲】</note><app n="0652020" word-count="8"><lem>也亦云八葉中臺也</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0652b04"/><p>次說<note n="0652021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">印＝身【甲】</note><app n="0652021"><lem>印</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">身</rdg></app>&CB00057;<note n="0652022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔印〕－【甲】</note><app n="0652022"><lem>印</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>二羽三補吒。戒方內掌來
<lb n="0652b05"/>去。<note n="0652023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔&CB00057;曰〕－&M062485;【原】</note><sic n="0652023" corr="＆lac；" resp="【原】">&CB00057;曰</sic></p><p type="dharani">唵炎摩智利<app type="＊" source="0652011"><lem>娑婆賀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">沙呵</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0652b06"/><p>次說普供<note n="0652024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔養〕－【甲】</note><app n="0652024"><lem>養</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>印。二羽三補吒。禪智立來去</p>
<lb n="0652b07"/><p type="dharani">唵<note n="0652025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">喃＝布【甲】</note><app n="0652025"><lem>喃</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">布</rdg></app>惹摩尼<note n="0652026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">娑&CB00085;賀＝沙&CB01239;【甲】</note><app n="0652026"><lem>娑&CB00085;賀</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">沙&CB01239;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0652b08"/><p>次總<note n="0652027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔說總〕－【甲】</note><app n="0652027"><lem>說總</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>印。二羽三補吒。進力<note n="0652028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔立〕－【甲】</note><app n="0652028"><lem>立</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>來去。&CB00057;
<lb n="0652b09"/>曰</p><p type="dharani">唵&CB03777;只&CB00135;耶<note n="0652029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">娑&CB00085;二合賀＝沙&CB01239;【甲】</note><app n="0652029"><lem>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>賀</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">沙&CB01239;</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0652b10"/><p>次請<note n="0652030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔讚〕－【甲】</note><app n="0652030"><lem>讚</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>印。二羽三補吒。進力來去次<note n="0652031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">撥＝&CB03751;【甲】</note><app n="0652031"><lem>撥</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB03751;</rdg></app>遣
<lb n="0652b11"/>以觀手禪進彈</p>
<lb n="0652b12"/><p>復說成就法。若念得大<note n="0652032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">福＝富【甲】</note><app n="0652032"><lem>福</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">富</rdg></app>德。持阿迦木護摩
<lb n="0652b13"/><note n="0652033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（滿）＋七【甲】</note><app n="0652033"><lem>七</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">滿七</rdg></app>萬遍。若念得五穀成就。以稻實華護摩。
<lb n="0652b14"/>若念他人福德。取得其家<note n="0652034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB01105;土＝&CB01105;五土取【甲】</note><app n="0652034"><lem>&CB01105;土</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB01105;五土取</rdg></app>護摩。若念得
<lb n="0652b15"/>高位<note n="0652035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">二＝高【甲】</note><app n="0652035"><lem>二</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">高</rdg></app>德。以比哩華護摩。若念生生世世怨
<lb n="0652b16"/>敵伏。以苦<note n="0652036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔練〕－【甲】</note><app n="0652036"><lem>練</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>木護摩。若念惡靈邪<note n="0652037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">家＝氣【甲】</note><app n="0652037"><lem>家</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">氣</rdg></app>伏。以
<lb n="0652b17"/>毒味護摩。若念顛狂<note n="0652038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">痾＝&CB00678;【甲】</note><app n="0652038"><lem>痾</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB00678;</rdg></app><note n="0652039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">病＋（及痔病）【甲】</note><app n="0652039"><lem>病</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">病及痔病</rdg></app>除愈。<note n="0652040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蓮＝連【甲】</note><app n="0652040"><lem>蓮</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">連</rdg></app><note n="0652041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">實＝寶&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0652041"><lem>實</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">寶</rdg></app>草
<lb n="0652b18"/>護摩。三萬遍。若念滅罪生善<note n="0652042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">生＝捨&M062485;【原】</note><sic n="0652042" corr="捨" resp="【原】">生</sic>身後生極
<lb n="0652b19"/>樂<note n="0652043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">以＋（迦）【甲】</note><app n="0652043"><lem>以</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">以迦</rdg></app>草護摩三萬遍。若念惡人&CB00057;咀還著本
<lb n="0652b20"/>人。以苦草投火中護摩三萬遍。若念得無量
<lb n="0652b21"/>榮果俸祿。<note n="0652044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">白華鳥＝白在以鳥【甲】</note><app n="0652044"><lem>白華鳥</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">白在以鳥</rdg></app>草護摩三萬遍。若念三昧
<lb n="0652b22"/>辨<note n="0652045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">財＝才【甲】</note><app n="0652045"><lem>財</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">才</rdg></app><note n="0652046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">德＝得【甲】</note><app n="0652046"><lem>德</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">得</rdg></app>者。以<note n="0652047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔骨〕－【甲】</note><app n="0652047"><lem>骨</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>婁草護摩三萬遍。若念化
<lb n="0652b23"/>度一切眾生令離苦得樂。以白芥子護摩三
<lb n="0652b24"/>萬遍。若念化度無佛世界眾生。以尸迦草護
<lb n="0652b25"/>摩三<note n="0652048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔七〕－&M062485;【原】</note><sic n="0652048" corr="＆lac；" resp="【原】">七</sic>萬遍。若念枯田&CB02770;五穀生者。加持
<lb n="0652b26"/>古蔓菁。加持<note n="0652049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">散＋（其所）【甲】</note><app n="0652049"><lem>散</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">散其所</rdg></app>。若愁萬病者。牛膝草護摩
<lb n="0652b27"/>三萬遍。若愁三陰四熱種種病。以降乾<note n="0652050" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">各＝天&M062485;【原】</note><sic n="0652050" corr="天" resp="【原】">各</sic>門
<lb n="0652b28"/>草護摩。若夫妻不和者。比<note n="0652051" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">罪＝羅【甲】</note><app n="0652051"><lem>罪</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">羅</rdg></app>草護摩三萬
<lb n="0652b29"/>遍和合。若惡友善友相違者。藤葉草護摩三
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1158.0652c" n="0652c"/>
<lb n="0652c01"/>萬遍。若白月八日十四日。十五日<note n="0652052" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔以〕－【甲】</note><app n="0652052"><lem>以</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>上法修
<lb n="0652c02"/>必得成就</p>
<lb n="0652c03"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead>地藏菩薩儀軌<note n="0652053" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此下甲本奧書曰永久五年七月二十三日書寫竟比校了</note></jhead></juan></div1>
